tool_description: MMAAPI is your ultimate source for the latest updates, scores, and results from the world of mixed martial arts. Our API covers all major MMA organizations, including UFC, Bellator, KSW, PFL, and many more.Our live scoring and real-time statistics provide a comprehensive view of every fight, making MMAAPI the go-to API to get MMA scores worldwide.
name: MMAAPI
title: MMAAPI

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: This operation allows you to search for MMA teams and tournaments based on the search term provided.

required_parameters.name: term
required_parameters.description: The search term to use when searching for teams and tournaments.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://mmaapi.p.rapidapi.com/api/mma/search/mcgregor"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "mmaapi.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
